e is delicious served warm with vanilla ice cream.","<strong>Quick chocolate cake<\/strong>: place chocolate into mixing bowl and grate <strong>5 sec\/speed 7<\/strong>. Add butter and melt <strong>4 min\/60°C\/speed 2<\/strong>. Add flour, sugar, salt and eggs and mix <strong>15 sec\/speed 5<\/strong>. Transfer into a springform cake tin (22 cm) and bake for approx. 20 minutes (180°C)."],"basicInfo":["medium","15m","40m","12 slices"]}